<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause id="_8667a205-5e85-472b-81a9-c5ff81c763c2" outputclass="ncc-clause" variation="SA"><meta><facet building="Class 1a"/><facet building="Class 1b"/><facet building="Class 2"/><facet building="Class 3"/><facet building="Class 4"/><facet building="Class 5"/><facet building="Class 6"/><facet building="Class 9a"/><facet building="Class 9b"/><facet building="Class 9c"/><facet building="Class 10a"/><facet building="Class 10b"/><facet building="Class 10c"/></meta><sptc>I3D1</sptc><title id="_06a6a9ef-ac90-45ed-8358-35f3c06bd2a5">Application of Part</title><archive-num>2019: SA H3.1</archive-num><subclause id="_bc27147d-1b14-4681-9248-c323921a14d8" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_688aaee6-32fb-4275-bf2c-44da7e747f11">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1236_1.0.0.xml#_2f02788f-8757-4689-b36e-e44d96524cc9" id="_56f01569-d86d-450c-869a-14dc52ecd8ba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions</xref> of this Part apply to <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1271_2.5.0.xml#_0dbf918d-9dc3-4d70-9eb8-7172ea21c7a1" id="_8fd65d2a-b70c-469d-a83d-d4f02a5b959c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">farm buildings</xref> in South Australia.</p></subclause><subclause id="_5197e90d-11ec-4300-8980-4d6c772282ca" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_2410e02f-b865-40a9-8a92-ffc417427779">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>The <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1236_1.0.0.xml#_2f02788f-8757-4689-b36e-e44d96524cc9" id="_47632c19-5056-4611-9bac-953035121d19" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions</xref> of this Part take precedence where there is a difference to the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1236_1.0.0.xml#_2f02788f-8757-4689-b36e-e44d96524cc9" id="_45af477d-ad5a-48e9-996b-507eae229a28" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions</xref> of Sections C, D, E and F.</p></subclause><callout id="_1951409e-1d93-4aa6-80c7-ab5f89c83013"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><p>Part I3 contains <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1236_1.0.0.xml#_2f02788f-8757-4689-b36e-e44d96524cc9" id="_2a1294f0-1e8c-42b4-8524-814b3979fb7d" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Deemed-to-Satisfy Provisions</xref> additional to those contained in Sections C, D, E and F for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1271_2.5.0.xml#_0dbf918d-9dc3-4d70-9eb8-7172ea21c7a1" id="_785fb39e-7f78-4181-82dd-3d2c9ed34af2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">farm buildings</xref>.</p><p>The standard NCC definition and provisions for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1272_2.0.0.xml#_9f1c1558-afbd-4a7a-a1b8-ae860e3b2ccd" id="_badc93f4-1f9c-47d1-b434-34a15591d866" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">farm sheds</xref> do not apply in South Australia. All buildings that meet the SA definition of <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/8bd50c59-637c-4a79-8565-09cd674ed7ed/1271_2.5.0.xml#_0dbf918d-9dc3-4d70-9eb8-7172ea21c7a1" id="_de598337-8389-45ef-bc46-cfa1eba93103" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="glossterm">farm buildings</xref> must comply with Part I3.</p></callout></clause>